---
title: How to
blog: travel_articles
---
<main>

<section class="section--introduction bg-gray-light text-blue-dark px-4">
  <div class="container mx-auto xl:px-32 xxl:px-48 pt-12">
    <p class="text-xl xl:text-3xl mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-tight">Pledging not to fly can seem daunting if you don't know where to start. Our 'how to' articles can help you get cracking, with ideas for travel destinations, and everything from tips on travelling with children, to guidance on how to talk to the people around you about your pledge.</p>
    <h1 class="text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4 md:mb-10">How to</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto xl:px-32 xxl:px-48 pb-12">
    <ul class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 ff-bullets">
      <%- data.how_to_links.primary.links.each do |link| -%>
      <li class="py-1 sm:py-2 md:py-4 flex items-center"><span class="inline-block xs:mx-2"><%= partial "svg/dot_pink.svg" %></span><a href="<%= link.url %>" target="_blank" class="ml-1 md:ml-4 text-xl xl:text-3xl hover:text-orange"><%= link.text %></a></li>
      <%- end -%>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto xl:px-32 xxl:px-48">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4 md:mb-10">How to travel</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="container mx-auto xl:px-32 xxl:px-48 pb-12">
    <ul class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 ff-bullets">
      <%- data.how_to_links.secondary.links.each do |link| -%>
      <li class="py-1 sm:py-2 md:py-4 flex items-center"><span class="inline-block xs:mx-2"><%= partial "svg/dot_blue.svg" %></span><a href="<%= link.url %>" target="_blank" class="ml-1 md:ml-4 text-xl xl:text-3xl hover:text-orange"><%= link.text %></a></li>
      <%- end -%>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section--articles-travel bg-orange text-blue-dark px-4">
  <div class="container mx-auto xl:px-32 xxl:px-48 pt-12 pb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-10">Destination inspiration</h2>
    <p class="text-xl xl:text-3xl mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-tight">Be inspired by these stories of overland travel. If you have a story of flight-free travel to share, please <a href="mailto:info@flightfree.co.uk" class="border-b-4 border-blue hover:text-blue">get in touch</a>.</p>
    <%= partial "articles", locals: { articles: blog.articles } %>
  </div>
</section>

</main>
